  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b93\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc7 \u0b9a\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "National buildings should be handed over to security forces - Omalbe Sobitha Thera",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Once President Gotabaya Rajapaksa steps down, the protesters must hand over the national buildings, namely the Presidential Palace, the Presidential Secretariat and the Alari Palace, to the security forces.",
        "Omalbe Sobitha Thera said that the general public should cooperate to take a decision in the political framework regarding the next step.",
        "He mentioned the above while attending a press conference held in Colombo on Tuesday 12th.",
        "The President is now facing the consequences of acting arbitrarily to win everything with a two-thirds majority. The entire country has suffered due to the mismanagement of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna.",
        "People's struggle against President Gotabaya Rajapaksa has won. It has been confirmed that even Ekshakti cannot stand in the face of public opposition. In Sri Lanka's political history, no head of state has been so opposed by the people.",
        "As soon as President Gotabaya Rajapaksa steps down, the protesters must hand over the National Buildings - the Presidential Palace, the Presidential Secretariat and the Alari Palace - to security. Attention should be paid to the next steps following the resignation of the President.",
        "The economic crisis will never be solved if there are continuous protests in the country. Common people should cooperate to overcome all crisis. He said that the pressing demand of the people for the resignation of the President has succeeded."
      ],
